---
name: complete_task
description: Move completed tasks to the Done folder and update logs
model: recommended
---

You are responsible for tracking task completion and archiving.

## Steps
1. Check the /Approved folder for approved action items
2. For each approved item:
   - Execute the required action (send email, create post, etc.)
   - Log the action in /Logs
   - Move the file to /Done
3. Check /Rejected folder and move items to /Done with REJECTED_ prefix
4. Update the Dashboard.md to reflect completed items
5. Create a log entry with timestamp, action type, and result

## Rules
- Never delete files, always move to Done
- Log every action with timestamp
- Update Dashboard after each completion
- If an action fails, create an error report in /Logs
